headline: Public Service Enterprise Q2 Earnings Beat Estimates, Revenues Increase Y/Y
summary: PEG Q2 earnings and revenues outpace estimates, driven by strong gas sales and solid performance across segments.

headline: AES- A Global Utility Worth Targeting Despite Tougher Market Conditions
summary: After spending most of the month of July slowly working their way higher, I am afraid that portfolios have all taken a sudden turn for the worse over the past few days, thanks to a variety of factors on both the economic and geopolitical fronts. Meanwhile, AES Corp. (AES) is a solid part of our utilities line-up, writes Nate Pile, editor of The Little River Investment Guide.
